{"tid":1623271,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"為美國製造制裁名單  快d參選區議會選舉","createTime":"2019-10-04T19:27:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-15T19:25:12.000Z","uid":89160,"like":28,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"0d734a4a04bfc70a305dd33b9f63ff6fe02098c8","tid":1623271,"uid":89160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T19:27:24.000Z","msg":"岩岩陳浩天提出左一個好好既方法，就係參選區議會。<br />\n<br />\n我覺得若果有人唔怕出面，可以試下候選，而又同時做呢幾樣野：<br />\n1. 主張港獨<br />\n2. 政綱係「光復香港，時代革命」、唱過「願榮光歸香港」<br />\n3. 主張香港自決前途<br />\n4. 話自己支持本土民主前線、香港眾志、香港民族黨<br />\n5. 主張香港擺脫北京干預，實行完整自治<br />\n<br />\n做過以上一兩項野，咁係幾乎肯定會畀人DQ，<strong><ins><span style=\"color: orange;\">咁選舉主任畀你既DQ信就係制裁既物證！</span></ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n區議會選舉按金係3000蚊，理論上要畀返你，就算唔賴皮唔畀你都係3000蚊。區議會選舉主任有18個，即係最少要18個人參加。如果你驚畀泛民話你𠝹票，你咪揀個冇泛民既選區，甚至講明入到閘都唔宣傳，反而唔係志在搶位。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>提名期去到10月17號，只需要10個當區選民提名</strong></span></span>，等待18個肯出樣既義士！<br />\n<br />\n區議會選舉主任名單<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.elections.gov.hk/dc2019/pdf/2019_DCE_Contact_Methods.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.elections.gov.hk%2Fdc2019%2Fpdf%2F2019_DCE_Contact_Methods.pdf&d=Bs0XXOgOekCAei%2FiISrrFrvH1KbbL%2ByyGPsbuV3zdoQ%3D&h=1d4a46d3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.elections.gov.hk/dc2019/pdf/2019_DCE_Contact_Methods.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n陳浩天原post<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hotin.chan.9277/posts/10158815648185130\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhotin.chan.9277%2Fposts%2F10158815648185130&d=Bs0XXOgOekCAei%2FiISrrFrvH1KbbL%2ByyGPsbuV3zdoQ%3D&h=17605a78\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hotin.chan.9277/posts/10158815648185130</a>"},{"pid":"3aa4a670d5cb8200ac0fa633ffb0fffc3898b17e","tid":1623271,"uid":89160,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T19:37:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>選舉主任 黃何詠詩、陳天柱、陳尚文、馬周佩芬